{"id":113747,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/简讯：北京灭门案凶手被判死刑/","date":"2010-10-15T23:10:53Z","modified":"2010-10-15T23:10:53Z","title":"简讯：北京灭门案凶手被判死刑","content":"<div>\n<p>震动中国的北京大兴“灭门案”的凶手一审被判处死刑。</p>\n<p>30岁男子李磊在2009年11月23日杀死了自己的妻子、两个孩子以及父母和妹妹。</p>\n<p>他作案后逃亡，后在海南被捕。</p>\n<p>法院同时判处他向死者的亲属做出343万元人民币经济赔偿。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hj8K5LB6EW0Y3RuiDWZoTUfdF3U/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hj8K5LB6EW0Y3RuiDWZoTUfdF3U/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hj8K5LB6EW0Y3RuiDWZoTUfdF3U/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hj8K5LB6EW0Y3RuiDWZoTUfdF3U/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Llk2CV3G0no:Iq450AVgl_U:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Llk2CV3G0no:Iq450AVgl_U:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Llk2CV3G0no:Iq450AVgl_U:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Llk2CV3G0no:Iq450AVgl_U:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Llk2CV3G0no:Iq450AVgl_U:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Llk2CV3G0no:Iq450AVgl_U:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/Llk2CV3G0no\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/10/10